Author: akamit-account-hacked
Title: [Bounty] Mfun - ⚡⚡ Disrupting the Digital Economy ⚡⚡ | $1,750,000 Reward To Pay
Body: The Mfun bounty campaign has been paused, effective from 4th Sep 2018. It is because Mfun is moving to new tech, they will have a new token economy, and they have a new plan.  Mfun is pausing the campaign for someday and will resume with another new bounty campaign some days later from now. They don't have an exact date yet but said soon. The token allocation will remain same, they have confirmed to me that. The current campaign and the new campaign will have the same allocation which is $1.75m. The figure is for the entire bounty campaign (Current one and the new one).  If you want you can continue to participate in the new campaign and can add up your current stakes with the new one. But if you do not participate in the new campaign, no matter, your current earnings will be kept and will be rewarded as they have promised.  Most probably, the new campaign will be managed by a new bounty manager or by Mfun team. I'm unable to continue anymore because of my busy schedules.  I will update the stakes for the 13 weeks of the current spreadsheets and transfer to Mfun team, they will continue from there.  If you have any questions related to the campaign or anything else then please contact at this email id info@mfun.io or join their official telegram group https://t.me/mfuntoken or their bounty group https://t.me/bounty_mfun  If you have any question related to the stakes or you want to do any change then shoot me a pm before 12th Sep. After 12th Sep I will not accept any request.

Author: akamit
Title: [Bounty] Mfun - ⚡⚡ Disrupting the Digital Economy ⚡⚡ | $1,750,000 Reward To Pay
Body: Update: Signature Codes Added. Interested participants can now wear the signature codes and join the campaign. Please find the codes in second post. And please make sure you read the rules.   Website | Announcement | Medium | Twitter | Telegram Official | Telegram Bounty   Mfun is starting its Official Bounty Program in order to reward its supporters with Mfun tokens.  MFUN team is offering 17,500,000 Mfun tokens for the Bounty Program which is worth $1,750,000 at the ICO price.  The bounty program will run until the end of the Token Sale. Bounty tokens will be distributed according to the number of stakes each bounty hunter has earned.       General Rules  Stakes will be distributed weekly. Bounty token distribution will take place 2-4 weeks after the ICO and it will be distributed by Mfun team.  Every user can register for the program only once, multiple accounts will be disqualified.  Bounty campaign members who use unfair methods such as spam, fake accounts, fake likes or fake shares, are to be excluded from bounty campaigns and will not receive any rewards.  Using multi-accounts, cheating, using someone else to do the work and spamming or any kind of unethical behavior when participating to one of the campaigns is not allowed and will get you disqualified from all bounties.  We reserve the rights to eliminate you if we think you have not been honest with your work.  We reserve the right to change bounty campaign rules at any given time.  Follower/Friend number cannot be change during the whole campaign period.  For any questions regarding the bounty campaign, please contact the bounty manager on the bounty telegram group: https://t.me/mfun_bounty  No KYC needed for Bounty Hunters.  All bounty participants are required to join MFUN’s Official Telegram group: https://t.me/mfun_official  NO REPORT OF SHARES AND POSTS IN THIS BOUNTY THREAD BEFORE AND AFTER THE GIVEN DATE OF EACH WEEK WILL BE COUNTED.   The first week starts on 4th June 2018 Week 1: 4th June to 10th June 2018 Week 2: 11th June to 17th June 2018 Week 3: 18th June to 24th June 2018 And so on….   Telegram Campaign   Join our Official Telegram (https://t.me/mfun_official) Group and Get 10 Stakes (You must stay in the group till ICO is over)  Add Text "www.mfun.io ICO" to your telegram username and get 10 Stakes (e.g. Jack - www.mfun.io ICO)  Add our Avatar to your Telegram profile picture and get 10 Stakes Avatar link: https://i.imgur.com/kYekQb4.jpg  Apply | Status   Signature Campaign  Distribution of stakes is according to user rank  Jr. Member: 1 stake/post Member: 2 stakes/post Full Member: 3 stakes/post Sr Member: 5 stakes/post Hero/Legendary: 7 stakes/post  Signature Campaign Rules  A minimum of 15 and a maximum of 30 meaningful posts will be accepted.  Posts on local boards are allowed but no more than 5 Posts.  Posts should not be made in bounties, off topic, archival, Beginners & Help, Meta and Politics & Society sections.  Participants must be at least a Jr.Member. Do not apply if you are not at least a Jr.Member.  Participants must be an active Bitcointalk user with no negative trust.  Signature, avatar and personal text must be kept during the entire period of campaign and until campaign manager asks you to remove.  Spam and Trolling is strictly not allowed.  Posts must have a minimum length of 75 characters.  Multiple accounts are not allowed and users found using more than one account will be disqualified.  If you get negative trust or banned from forum for whatever reasons, you will be disqualified and no stakes will be rewarded to you.  We will single-handedly check every post of every participant.  Do not fill the form without wearing our signature, avatar and personal text or you will be rejected.  If your rank changes during the campaign, please write a pm to the Bounty Manager with your spreadsheet number and new rank.  We reserve rights to make any changes in payment and Terms of this campaign.  Get signature codes from the second post  Apply | Status   Translation & Moderation Campaign  All languages are welcome!  Whitepaper Translation: 500 Stakes  Translation of ANN thread + Bounty Thread: 500 Stakes  Moderation of Ann/bounty thread: 10 Stakes per Valid Post   How to Join Post in this thread to reserve your language, I will PM all eligible participants After being accepted and completing the translation, fill the form below with the link to the translated threads.  Rules We are looking for Jr. Members or above.  You are required to complete the translation in 7 days. Failure to complete it on time will lead to the stakes being rewarded in half.  Translators must update Ann/Bounty thread by making at least 4 posts per week  Spam post will not be counted  We prefer 1 person per language to handle all the tasks (Ann Thread + Bounty Thread + Whitepaper + Moderation)  Submit | Status   Twitter Campaign  Stakes will be paid depending on followers (at the start of the campaign).  250+ followers: 1 stake per tweet/retweet 1000+ followers: 2 stakes per tweet/retweet 5000+ followers: 4 stakes per tweet/retweet 10.000+ followers: 6 stakes per tweet/retweet   Rules All participants must follow our official Twitter account: https://twitter.com/mfunofficial  Your audit score must be more than 85% according to https://www.twitteraudit.com  Your Twitter account must be mainly about cryptocurrencies, or gaming. We will also accept media personalities.  You need at least 250 real followers to participate.  Minimum 5 tweets/retweets and maximum 20 tweets/retweets per week will be counted.  Tweets/Retweets must be spaced at least for 1 hour and a maximum of 4 tweets/retweets are allowed per day.  If there is no tweet on our official twitter account, please make your own tweets instead.  Follower number cannot be changed during the campaign.  You should edit your first report to add your next reports. Don’t create new posts for new weeks, it will not be counted.   Requirements Tweets and retweets must have a link to the MFUN’s website (https://mfun.io) or Official Telegram group (https://t.me/mfun_official) Tweets and retweets must have at least 2 of these hashtags: #MFUN #gaming #ICO #Blockchain #cryptocurrency #presale #tokensale   Apply | Status   Report Format: (Replace X with week number) Code: Twitter Week X Spreadsheet number: Twitter Account Link: List of Tweets and Retweets:   Video Campaign  Youtube, Facebook, Dailymotion, Vimeo or any other kinds of video platform with a significant number of social outreach and are mainly about cryptocurrencies will be accepted.  Rules Videos must be longer than 2 minutes.  Videos have to be meaningful and related to MFUN. They should be descriptive. Videos with music will not be accepted. Speech must be made by a real person, videos edited with the help of voice synthesizers will not be accepted.  Videos with fake views will be disqualified.  Videos must be in English or Bahasa Indonesia or Mandarin.  Youtube channels must have at least 100 organic subscribers.  Facebook groups, pages or profile must have 500 members, likes, friends/followers.  The video has to be of good quality.  You can submit multiple videos, but it needs to be different and video posting platforms need to be different as well.  All videos will be reviewed by the manager. Low quality or offensive material will be disqualified. Decisions taken by the Bounty Team are final and non-negotiable.  We consider different measures to judge the best quality video, includes views, audience reach etc. Stakes for the videos will be given based on quality:  Rejected: 0 Stake Low Quality: 10 Stakes Medium Quality: 20 stakes High Quality: 30 Stakes  Submit | Status   Content Campaign  Medium/Steemit, Facebook/LinkedIn group/pages, ICO listing sites, Blog, News sites, forums with crypto audiences or any other social outlet with a large outreach are accepted.  Rules Must have at least 100 followers/members.  The blog/article must have original content. Copy/paste is not allowed. Plagiarism will lead to rejection and disqualification from the bounty campaign.  The content made must be publicly accessible.  Must have links to our website, whitepaper, Ann thread and official Telegram group.  Blogs/articles must have at least 400 words and forum posts must have at least 250 words.  Blogs/articles in languages other than English are also accepted but must inform the bounty manager beforehand.  Spamming/posting in wrong subforums will not be tolerated. Posts deleted or closed by the forum’s administration will not be counted.  Articles exceptionally are written will be used and posted by MFUN.  Articles with fake views will be disqualified.  All articles/blogs/posts submitted for bounty will be reviewed by MFUN Bounty Team and will be rewarded based on quality:  Rejected: 0 Stake Low Quality: 10 Stakes Medium Quality: 20 stakes High: 30 Stakes  Submit | Status   Scammer Check Bounty  Users who have used more than one account to sign up for bounty and/or users who have used weekly reports which are not their own and/or any other kind of scam you notice in this bounty program must be reported to us with proof. We will verify it and reward you with stakes.  Please note that false accusations will lead to your own disqualification.  Rewards 10 stakes for spotting a Scam  Report Here | Status   Disclaimer We are hired by the Mfun team to manage the bounty community and the spreadsheets only. All the tokens will be distributed by the Mfun team at the end of the token sale.
